title: Google\Cloud\Compute\V1\VpnGatewayStatusVpnConnection
name: VpnGatewayStatusVpnConnection
description:
A VPN connection contains all VPN tunnels connected from this VpnGateway to the same peer gateway. The peer gateway could either be a external VPN gateway or GCP VPN gateway.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.compute.v1.VpnGatewayStatusVpnConnection

Extends Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.peer_external_gateway
params.description: URL reference to the peer external VPN gateways to which the VPN tunnels in this VPN connection are connected. This field is mutually exclusive with peer_gcp_gateway.

params.name: data.peer_gcp_gateway
params.description: URL reference to the peer side VPN gateways to which the VPN tunnels in this VPN connection are connected. This field is mutually exclusive with peer_gcp_gateway.

params.name: data.tunnels
params.description: List of VPN tunnels that are in this VPN connection.
